/-- Strict visible-spike density deficit in the form `< 1 - saving / denom`.
This is the general shell-spike output once the requested saving is below the
predicted good-shell gain. -/
theorem OrderedShadowBigCertificate.visibleSpike_upperDensityLessThan
    {Hlog u vseq H V : ℕ → ℝ} {tau x saving denom : ℝ}
