/-- Fully expanded normalized-budget-to-measure-improvement wrapper.
This theorem is intentionally verbose: it shows exactly which inputs remain. -/
theorem oneOverPi_irratMeasure_lt_of_Bauer_normalizedOrderedBudget_big
